text: "Roman's Revenge" is a hip-hop song by Nicki Minaj featuring Eminem, released on October 30, 2010. It is from Minaj's debut studio album, Pink Friday. This song initiated a feud between Nicki Minaj and Lil' Kim and also is a diss towards Lil' Kim. ==References== Category:2010 songs Category:Nicki Minaj songs Category:Eminem songs Category:Diss tracks Category:Hip hop songs
